{"tid":1087503,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突發有圖 出pool有望啦","createTime":"2019-04-01T11:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T23:53:53.000Z","uid":146934,"like":1049,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"37dae1fc3cdaaa0fa15825c9afb7af0a649761af","tid":1087503,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"話說返緊711便利店pt<br />\n突然有個學生妹含情蜜蜜咁望住我<br />\n就係電光火石之間我地眼神通電咗3秒<br />\n<br />\n過咗5分鐘之後佢過黎收銀機畀錢<br />\n再口窒窒咁同我講「唔...該...我想...eps攞500啊...」<br />\n然後 我再望望佢買咗20蚊野<br />\n500+20=520=我愛你😍😍😍<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我嘅初戀會喺711咁平淡地出現<br />\n<br />\n我都有懷疑過係咪我ff太多<br />\n但憑佢第一眼嘅眼神就睇得出佢對我嘅傾慕<br />\n<br />\n果然不出我所料<br />\n佢5分鐘之後再入黎買第二樣20蚊嘅貨再攞500<br />\n仲問我要返張單<br />\n我即刻喺張單度寫低我電話比佢<br />\n然後佢甜笑一下就離開咗...<br />\n<br />\n第一次同異性咁親密接觸<br />\n戀愛嘅心情真係好忑忐🥰🥰🥰<br />\n<br />\n想請教下 如果佢打過黎第一句我應該講咩好？😍😍😍"},{"pid":"9133491d35685eb55347f5bf399d17e9f5e4d080","tid":1087503,"uid":218575,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"15a4b959b117d6e91a47d642e67c163b4f76e32d","tid":1087503,"uid":146934,"like":1255,"dislike":12,"score":1243,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sqBMSSp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsqBMSSp.png&h=ad6723b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真人真事 絕對無老作"},{"pid":"9ff7b95e9decd1991a14ede3fd9c4ad9c2654492","tid":1087503,"uid":116910,"like":80,"dislike":5,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"問佢幾錢Q"},{"pid":"68c0884e7ef7f9be3cb363945f3bf2e509da7150","tid":1087503,"uid":55924,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"講咩好？<br />\n講死臭雞呀!"},{"pid":"9dfd50d4b6add9046d8b79a660506315a7cecaa8","tid":1087503,"uid":224533,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"人地嚟攞錢畀ptbf"},{"pid":"d17a58e87c136ae44749e0543b4f0e249a9813cb","tid":1087503,"uid":238697,"like":4,"di